Описание:
Greetings from our friendly and successful team of WGG Digital agency!
We are looking for candidates for the direction of SMM marketing. We need a candidate with a high level of English language skills who wants to work with our international clients remotely.
Friendly relations, achieving results at work and continuous development of employees are our core values. We are really good at helping businesses grow, for example, by increasing turnover 20 times in a year. Our clients include both middle and small businesses, as well as such giants as SAP, Visa Qiwi Wallet, Jaguar and others. We have been operating in the UAE, Saudi Arabia, Turkey and more than 30 other countries for 5 years.
We are always glad to see talented people in our team who want to build an international career!
Let's start with what we'll do for you:
Large, foreign and interesting projects to your portfolio;
The opportunity to develop professionally, our experienced mentors will prompt you and will always be there for you;
No bureaucracy, openness to suggestions and encouragement of initiative;
The opportunity to work with all existing niches - from personal brands to large manufacturing companies.;
We will also provide an opportunity for rapid career growth - we have a system for evaluating your development, and you can grow from an intern to the head of your own team.
What will you do:
Create SMM strategies for agency clients under the guidance of an experienced strategist;
Generate content: write texts, select and design photos;
Participate in the organization of photo shoots;
Moderate official communities (on behalf of brands);
Conduct daily analytics, collect statistics and keep reports.
What do we expect from you:
Knowledge and use of English at least B2 level;
At least 6 months of experience in SMM;
Experience in making reels and writing scripts;
Ready-made visual portfolio;
The ability to express your thoughts correctly verbally and in writing;
The opportunity to work full-time;
The desire to develop in the field of SMM marketing;
The ability to quickly dive into complex topics;
Prompt decision-making in crisis situations;
Stress resistance;
Good mood, because it is very important for our team :)
The conditions that we offer you:
Interesting international projects;
The opportunity to grow quickly;
Five days, from 10:00 to 19:00 Dubai time;
Remote working format;
Education at the agency's SMM school (theory and practice of marketing, SMM and PR)
Clear grades with salary increases.

